==[[Scottish Gaelic]]==

===Adjective===
'''Ruadh'''.
* [[Red]], [[auburn]], [[carroty]].
* Of [[hair]], [[redhead|redheaded]]. 
#:''"'S e rìbhinn ruadh mhaiseach a th'innte." ("It is a fair red-haired [[maiden]] that she is")''

